        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="企业架构系列"><a href="#企业架构系列" class="headerlink" title="企业架构系列"></a>企业架构系列</h3><div class="tip info"><p>企业架构可以分为两大部分  <strong>业务架构</strong> 和 <strong>IT架构</strong>，大部分企业架构方法都是从IT架构发展而来的。</p></div><h5 id="下面是企业架构的文章"><a href="#下面是企业架构的文章" class="headerlink" title="下面是企业架构的文章"></a>下面是企业架构的文章</h5><ul><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Kxr2-efQz-w8oiygnmat3g">企业架构的本质</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484442&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d5cd9c4f16f6be51de627265f90f9cad&amp;chksm=ec702adfdb07a3c98b1217355a907006ba2a13adfcf18a16f37fde40a20ab6c0494c42456032&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">企业架构的本质二</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484452&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=47eb3059d918269575af527aa4ae6a11&amp;chksm=ec702ae1db07a3f7e0b58304c205ae2aece3568c0544a1836cc4890c723a2cf0ddf975597966&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">企业架构工件</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484144&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=83a6131cbb60091a3528da3fa5c6b69c&amp;chksm=ec702c35db07a523892121a96e9eeea1371d7d969243899f96e5da5ca752d05851a50a2c4595&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">数据架构</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484647&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ccb22846a8c722d5fc089dc0a8b3abc6&amp;chksm=ec702a22db07a33482ac385377236d8b8bf0b988e0ee3b2bbfba5f72017707dd3d9b80a8fcfd&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2521095084893814785#rd">现代企业架构-技术架构</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484746&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8ca2ea8dfcf618b1634b08638ca49869&amp;chksm=ec702b8fdb07a299696d31afa5e48704e9ff962785ddd64a078a20ff1a3ed3af6f4e1734db38&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2521095084893814785#rd">架构视图和视角</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484828&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a999bf2161f52d429596cdd37adcd523&amp;chksm=ec702b59db07a24fdef3ae8c2392bcd94ad0e2194de502ed64fd9aa3e501149fccd018abe143&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2521095084893814785#rd">业务模型和业务架构的关系</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484934&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a309b9f085df6972435e983dda72988a&amp;chksm=ec7028c3db07a1d519cf904fc52f95bb7428f8aabccc70ddaad9d37c80dd342d2e5da322780f&amp;cur_album_id=2521095084893814785&amp;scene=189#wechat_redirect">双模交付在混合企业架构中的实践</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484369&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a6bdaacf85856c98c32e7e9ede3b2ba9&amp;chksm=ec702d14db07a40279c325d2f324c12a7ad74d89cf706204b8a777ae854b6fd69dfa61cd7c57&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2553438735867068418#rd">在架构开发方法中应用迭代</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484575&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1b800a7c992fc142b5d9518f518da25b&amp;chksm=ec702a5adb07a34c0893f8b5ef2f58cda5028bb197ba1ebf7d19b5721c2c0a51a97dda1484d0&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2521095084893814785#rd">如何进行系统设计</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484386&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b46d9d1abdb60a3682a0181dbc2c6802&amp;chksm=ec702d27db07a431829470776194ba1abd4db948ef9747a562805303b67d88f671961f91a321&amp;scene=178&amp;cur_album_id=2553438735414083585#rd">业务能力</a></li><li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5MzQ4NTQ4Mg==&amp;mid=2247484460&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=6c942411c46ba6b9fd9af64e4d5d50d4&amp;chksm=ec702ae9db07a3ff9b0ce1d08c4aa33129bcaa6590eaa8b50d20a055b9305508ad815f79e990&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect">架构原则-业务原则</a></li></ul><h4 id="扩展阅读"><a href="#扩展阅读" class="headerlink" title="扩展阅读"></a>扩展阅读</h4><ol><li><a href="../post/c0e93fbc.html">IT架构管控</a></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
